{"tid":1828653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自由鳥：外遊數據卡 買1送1（17-23/1）","createTime":"2020-01-18T04:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T16:21:52.000Z","uid":173951,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd0de45765432ca87f3133b39f6f4ca15f87d63","tid":1828653,"uid":173951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"應該好多人唔知<br />\n今朝買左六張，全部8月27到期<br />\n惠康門市都有，唔一定要上網買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於1月17日至1月23日期間，惠康、Market Place by Jason、3hreesixty、Jasons及網上商店^購買自由鳥遨遊SIM「亞洲12地」5日外遊數據卡可享買一送一優惠*，即係HK$75有2張！<br />\n*數量有限，售完即止。<br />\n<br />\n#「亞洲12地」包括中國、日本 、台灣、南韓、泰國、澳門、印尼、馬來西亞、新加坡、孟加拉、柬埔寨及斯里蘭卡。<br />\n<br />\n^網上商店: <a href=\"http://www.wellcome.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wellcome.com.hk%2F&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=45125b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wellcome.com.hk/</a> 、<a href=\"https://www.marketplacebyjasons.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketplacebyjasons.com&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=94a3ee46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.marketplacebyjasons.com</a>"},{"pid":"03740707e3d419fd337e437f9228fb2a60f6c0c1","tid":1828653,"uid":173951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"848eeb9f3170f59fdb84feed7d6e51ac03515aef","tid":1828653,"uid":190406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"拉 上一頁"},{"pid":"96cf0652eab706daac29f8b730a6c298a1df8948","tid":1828653,"uid":173951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e89c5ba695bd9fd8250b62ddbfbc22cff9867a01","tid":1828653,"uid":189972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T19:01:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c02e6e6c8ee410052919c6e5796496a789ab418f","tid":1828653,"uid":308167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"